title: va Cool 50s
description:
"Cool 50's" Contains rare, wild and weird songs from the 1950's. Proving that IT was the wackiest decade on record! This is a self made mix containing many genre's. Spoken Word, Rock n Roll, RnB, Jazz, Country, Soundtracks, Exotica, and Lounge. You will relive the variety: the sound of the 50's. ENJOY!
